                        </div>
                    </div>
                </aside>

                <!-- Right Content Area -->
                <div class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-8">
                    
                    <!-- Professional Experience -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Professional Experience</h2>
                        <div class="space-y-6 border-l-2 border-slate-200 ml-2">
                            <!-- Nike -->
                            <div class="relative pl-8">
                                <div class="absolute -left-[11px] top-1 h-5 w-5 bg-blue-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white"></div>
                                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium">June 2022 - Current</p>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800">Global Product Director, Supply Chain</h3>
                                <p class="text-md font-medium text-slate-600 mb-2">Nike WHQ</p>
                                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-600 text-sm space-y-1">
                                    <li>Led product org for >$2B global freight spend.</li>
                                    <li>Improved container mix by 32% YoY via new platforms.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <!-- Walmart -->
                             <div class="relative pl-8">
                                <div class="absolute -left-[11px] top-1 h-5 w-5 bg-blue-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white"></div>
                                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium">Aug 2021 - June 2022</p>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800">Director, Optimization & Central Control</h3>
                                <p class="text-md font-medium text-slate-600 mb-2">Walmart</p>
                                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-600 text-sm space-y-1">
                                    <li>Realized $65M in savings in FY22.</li>
                                    <li>Enabled $22M in savings via Blue Yonder TMS strategy.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <!-- Caterpillar -->
                            <div class="relative pl-8">
                                <div class="absolute -left-[11px] top-1 h-5 w-5 bg-blue-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white"></div>
                                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-medium">Feb 2017 - Oct 2019</p>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800">Manager, Network Analytics & Business Technology</h3>
                                <p class="text-md font-medium text-slate-600 mb-2">Caterpillar Inc.</p>
                                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-600 text-sm space-y-1">
                                    <li>Delivered >$20M in freight cost reduction.</li>
                                    <li>Reduced inventory by $11M through system alerts.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Interactive AI Tools -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                        <div class="mb-4 border-b border-gray-200">
                            <nav class="flex -mb-px" aria-label="Tabs">
                                <button class="tab-btn active w-1/2 py-4 px-1 text-center border-b-2 font-medium text-sm" data-tab="ai-strategy">
                                    ✨ AI Strategy Simulator
                                </button>
                                <button class="tab-btn w-1/2 py-4 px-1 text-center border-b-2 font-medium text-sm text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 hover:border-gray-300" data-tab="ai-contact">
                                    ✨ AI Q&A / Contact
                                </button>
                            </nav>
                        </div>

                        <!-- AI Strategy Tab Content -->
                        <div id="ai-strategy-content" class="tab-content">
                             <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 text-sm">Describe a supply chain challenge and get an instant, AI-powered strategic approach based on my experience.</p>
                             <textarea id="strategy-prompt" rows="4" class="w-full p-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500" placeholder="e.g., 'High international freight costs and poor container utilization...'"></textarea>
                             <button id="get-strategy-btn" class="mt-4 w-full btn-primary text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">Get AI Strategic Advice</button>
                        </div>

                        <!-- AI Contact Tab Content -->
                        <div id="ai-contact-content" class="tab-content hidden">
                            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4 text-sm">Ask the AI a question about my experience, or send me a message directly.</p>
                            <textarea id="question" name="question" rows="4" class="w-full p-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500" placeholder="e.g., 'What was the biggest challenge implementing the JDA TMS?'" required></textarea>
                            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mt-4">
